metadata.name: AE_1891 #1-7
metadata.description:
The owner of the NFT receives:

1. A unique NFT created between 02/19/2020 - 07/30/2022 and consisting of 1891 separate NFTs, each of which is a training video of one large course in Adobe After Effects
2. 1891 individual NFTs to upload to their collection
3. Access to a large course on the Adobe After 

Effects program, with which you can create NFTs
The proceeds will be used to develop training in computer graphics, animation, special effects.
